"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.14.1.4\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.14.1.4</span> 標題：庫房、銀庫、寶庫（treasury, strongroom）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： אֲרוֹן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ’aron)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:10\">2KI 12:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:11\">2KI 12:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:8\">2CH 24:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:10\">2CH 24:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:11\">2CH 24:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:11\">2CH 24:11</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： בַּיִת, אָסֹף</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： (beyth) ’asupim)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr26:15\">1CH 26:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr26:17\">1CH 26:17</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： בַּיִת, אוֹצָר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： (beyth) ’otsar)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:12\">DEU 28:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:34\">DEU 32:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:19\">JOS 6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:24\">JOS 6:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:51\">1KI 7:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:18\">1KI 15:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:18\">1KI 15:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:19\">2KI 12:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs14:14\">2KI 14:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs16:8\">2KI 16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:15\">2KI 18:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:13\">2KI 20:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:15\">2KI 20:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:13\">2KI 24:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:13\">2KI 24:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr9:26\">1CH 9:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr26:20\">1CH 26:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr26:20\">1CH 26:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr26:22\">1CH 26:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr26:24\">1CH 26:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr26:26\">1CH 26:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr27:25\">1CH 27:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr27:25\">1CH 27:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:12\">1CH 28:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:12\">1CH 28:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:8\">1CH 29:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:1\">2CH 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr8:15\">2CH 8:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:9\">2CH 12:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:9\">2CH 12:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:2\">2CH 16:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:24\">2CH 25:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:27\">2CH 32:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra2:69\">EZR 2:69</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:69\">NEH 7:69</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:70\">NEH 7:70</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh10:39\">NEH 10:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:21\">PRO 8:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:4\">EZK 28:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan1:2\">DAN 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:15\">HOS 13:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:10\">MAL 3:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： בַּיִת, נְכֹאת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： beth nkoth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:13\">2KI 20:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa39:2\">ISA 39:2</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Aramaic</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">蘭：גְּנַז</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： gnaz)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:20\">EZR 7:20</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： גֶּנֶז</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： genez)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth3:9\">EST 3:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth4:7\">EST 4:7</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： גַּנְזַךְ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ganzak)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:11\">1CH 28:11</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： γαζοφυλάκιον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： gazofulakion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:41\">MRK 12:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:41\">MRK 12:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:43\">MRK 12:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:1\">LUK 21:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:20\">JHN 8:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc3:28\">1MA 3:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc14:49\">1MA 14:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc3:6\">2MA 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc3:24\">2MA 3:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc3:28\">2MA 3:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc3:40\">2MA 3:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc4:42\">2MA 4:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc5:18\">2MA 5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc4:3\">4MA 4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc4:6\">4MA 4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd5:44\">1ES 5:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd8:18\">1ES 8:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd8:44\">1ES 8:44</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： θησαυρός</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： thēsauros)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir1:25\">SIR 1:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc3:29\">1MA 3:29</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： κορβανᾶς</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： korbanas)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:6\">MAT 27:6</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： ταμιεῖον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： tamieion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir29:12\">SIR 29:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： θησαυρός</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： thesaurus)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc4:7\">4MA 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Esd6:40\">2ES 6:40</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/PTZ-0075_pinnacle_hant.jpg\" alt=\"聖殿山的西南角\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">聖殿山的西南角 (© Ray Pritz by United Bible Societies)</figcaption></figure>寶庫是用來存放君王或其他國家行政機構的貴重物品的地方。耶路撒冷聖殿有自己的庫房。庫房沒有標準的大小或結構。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:10\">2KI 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:11\">2KI 12:11</a> 和（《和》12:9–10）<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:8\">2CH 24:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:10\">2CH 24:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:11\">2CH 24:11</a> 中，希伯來文<em>’aron</em> 指的是一個很大的奉獻箱。根據<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:10\">2KI 12:10</a> （《和》12:9），這種箱子的「門」上開有一個洞。「門」指的是箱子的一個表面，可能是箱子的頂面。以色列人可以把他們的捐項（不是硬幣，因為當時還沒有發明出來），通過這個洞塞到箱子裡面。之後，打開或取下箱子的頂，就可以取出捐項。</p>\n<p>在一些經文中，希伯來文<em>’otsar</em> 指的是寶物（treasure；如<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:13\">2KI 24:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:9\">2CH 12:9</a> ）；而在另一些經文中，這個詞指的是儲存寶物的地方，即庫房（treasury；如<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:13\">2KI 20:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:27\">2CH 32:27</a> ）。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:18\">1KI 15:18</a> 前半節的原文字面意思是：「亞撒取了耶和華殿的|u庫房|u*裡剩下的所有金銀，（他又取了）王宮中的|u寶物|u*」。我們所查閱的譯本都沒有區分這兩層意思，有些譯本把兩個詞都譯為「寶物」（“treasures”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ），還有譯本把它們都譯為「庫房」（“treasuries”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jewish Publication Society Version\">NJPSV</abbr> ）。事實上，在提到<em>’otsar</em> 的許多經文中，很難確定它的意思是「寶物」還是「庫房」。在希伯來文中，只有三處經文明確提到「寶物間」（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh10:39\">NEH 10:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan1:2\">DAN 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:10\">MAL 3:10</a> ）。</p>\n<p>如果目標語言沒有表示「庫房」的詞語，則可以使用描述性短語，例如，「存放／看守王（或聖殿）的貴重物品的地方）」。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:6\">MAT 27:6</a> 的後半節也可以譯成：「把它和聖殿的錢放在一起是違犯律法的，因為這是血錢。」</p>\n<p>在新約中，希臘文<em>gazofulakion</em> 也指一種用來收奉獻的箱子。根據猶太傳統，聖殿中有13個這樣的奉獻箱，讓金錢滑到箱子裡面的開口是號角形或羊角形的。因此，錢幣掉進箱子裡的聲音非常響亮。在有些文化中，人們並不知道這種奉獻箱，或者最多只知道教堂裡傳來傳去收取奉獻的袋子。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:1\">LUK 21:1</a> 中，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 將這個詞譯為“Temple money box”（「聖殿錢箱」），並加上了以下附註：「猶太人敬拜場所內一種特殊的盒子，人們把他們獻給上帝的禮物放到裡面。」PV 使用了一個較長的譯法，意為：「專門裝它們（禮物）的地方。」</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
